            "ref": "step3",
            "preparation": "cooked",
            "name": "Cooked chicken livers"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "step4",
          "action": "Mix the livers with the onion before chopping them together. The best way to do this is with a meat grinder, processing the mixture twice to get the right texture.",
